{"tid":14633,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 你那太空艙 仲貴過租一間劏房","createTime":"2016-11-30T14:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:21:19.000Z","uid":45011,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d61f35d7f186210c97c4746ae04248e0f26d1b04","tid":14633,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:52:05.000Z","msg":"你那太空艙 仲貴過租一間劏房 <br />\n間格夠寬敞 床頭右腳又會相撞 <br />\n一天天蝸居生活亦被同化 <br />\n幾手私樓的一眾市民隨便亂咁劏 多得你 承受這監倉 <br />\n<br />\n隻腳冇得搲 痕到要典一典下被 <br />\n晚晚冇得搞 難為伴侶入這基地 <br />\n起身返工收工的生活何其疲憊 每日做黎受氣 <br />\n聽朝必須交租老細期糧又未出 慘過送死 <br />\n<br />\n樓奴難嚇退 長期不需 排定公屋的隊 <br />\n十年後捱窮就係到佢 永遠都飲鉛水 <br />\n捱窮捱到尾 成為負累 <br />\n冇地方 抱著一起安睡 <br />\n九八年 場熊市 瞬息過去 <br />\n<br />\n買米買衣架 連地鐵都只識得加 <br />\n要買我的家 難道就買落馬洲吧 <br />\n租緊的私樓升值猶如無窮無限 努力做牛做馬 <br />\n即使薪金可加到兩萬拿來住屋 點夠去玩<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br />\n<br />\n上集: 評瘋樓 (改 於心有愧) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=3469187&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMU%26message%3D3469187%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=25b9c2e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=3469187&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a> <br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲們多多支持小弟既 音樂x旅遊 專頁  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faamusictravel&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bd27611d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel</a> <br />\n<br />\nBlog: <a href=\"https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.wordpress.com%2F&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=60425e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com/</a> <br />\n<br />\nInstagram: aa.music.travel"},{"pid":"7aed6d6e4bb8550c27e4ac967ec78f0bbd491057","tid":14633,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"留爐難嚇退"},{"pid":"ed7bd6cda52d69935640407d92f006755289f658","tid":14633,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"a仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca73de0281384652f2540ac4c468f2468374b1dd","tid":14633,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解好似咁多人識我#sosad#"},{"pid":"05b16c9fac84c94ccc9a17913b66f33266fc02a1","tid":14633,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>a仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解好似咁多人識我#sosad#</blockquote><br />\n大紅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a219a21ceb19671a51e8a19824ab355e8afea68c","tid":14633,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"典一癲蝦披"},{"pid":"692a87f8245ff9e260b6f125a11bc082c4da7ef5","tid":14633,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"A仔 而家係咪2邊走?"},{"pid":"036c8ed49612450febbb0e32db08aa243c3540dd","tid":14633,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A仔 而家係咪2邊走?</blockquote><br />\nHKG個邊好似人流少左好多，有人接我D詞我都會繼續係個邊既"},{"pid":"8408894c2fbb0cd974a99d0f94af63087c700eca","tid":14633,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;a仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解好似咁多人識我#sosad#&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n大紅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而想我D認真歌出名多D"},{"pid":"fdc8b0f4c36a2b1a9d640e8a564bb1bcc86c1bd2","tid":14633,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>a仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解好似咁多人識我#sosad#</blockquote><br />\n大紅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而想我D認真歌出名多D</blockquote><br />\n談何容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2645e376f9a9d63d3ae7b462027eb44a878c547","tid":14633,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;a仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解好似咁多人識我#sosad#&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n大紅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n我反而想我D認真歌出名多D&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n談何容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對我而言唔易，因為我係寫詞方面對時事既觸覺係Lag機既，要追潮流我唔夠玩，我寫既都係一D比較耐既潮流(明將、港女呢D講左好多年)，其實都唔容易出到位<br />\n<br />\n無辦法架喇，令自己出左名先，自己所寫既野先可以比多D人睇到，始終我最鐘意寫既，唔係口水歌"},{"pid":"9f